gomodel:SYNGO_1468  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig 3&4: Synapsin III KO neurons show reduced inhibitory post synaptic currents (reduced IPSC amplitude) and normal glutamatergic EPSC amplitude. The size of the recycling pool of synaptic vesicles was increased, and synaptic depression of EPSCs was reduced. (No data of IPSC depression profile).. Experimental description: Methods: Generation of synapsin III knock-out mice" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9900-4233" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
